                <note rend="inline" type="source">701.9491/17: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in Iran</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dreyfus</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-02-25T13:00:00-04:00"
                            >February 25, 1942—1 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>43. Your no. 34, February 8, noon. Please make further inquiries of the Prime
                    Minister as to Iranian intentions respecting continued relations with Japan.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Welles</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
